window.__KB.push({"t": "CLAIM FORM FOR MAJOR DISEASE - ENCEPHALITIS Policy No. 保單編號： 重病保障索償表格 － 腦 炎 PART", "f": "C24.pdf", "s": "CLAIM FORM FOR MAJOR DISEASE - ENCEPHALITIS Policy No. 保單編號： 重病保障索償表格 － 腦 炎 PART II – This Attending Physician’s Statement must be completed by a qualified and registered physician at the insured’s expense 第二部份 – 本應診醫生報告必須由受保人自費聘請之合資格註冊醫生填寫 1. Name of Patient 病人姓名 2. I.D. Card No. 身份證號碼 3. Age 年齡 4. Are you the patient's usual medical attendant? 閣下是否病人之私人醫生？ No 否 Yes 是 If \"Yes\", give details 若「是」，請填寫有關資料。 Period of Consultation Past Health History 應診期間 病人過往健康情況 5. a) Date on which you first attended the patient for this disease (Encephalitis). 首次為病人診治是項病症（腦炎）之日期。 b) What was the symptom(s) experienced prior to the first consultation? And for how long? 病人首次求診前有何症狀？該等症狀已存在多久？ c) When was the patient informed of the diagnosis? (Please give exact date) 何時通知病人診斷結果？（請填寫準確日期） 6. Give full and exact details of the diagnosis. 請詳盡填寫確實診斷資料。 7. Had the patient any past history of the disease specified above or related illness? 病人過往曾否患有上述疾病或有關疾病？ No 否 Yes 有 If \"Yes\", give details 若「有」，請填寫有關資料。 Name of Attended Physician(s) Date of Consultation Address(es) Exact Diagnosis 應診醫生姓名 診治日期 地址 確實診斷資料 8. Is there anything in the patient's family history which would have increased the risk of Encephalitis? 病人之家庭背景有否任何增加病人患上腦炎機會之事項？ 9. Please give details of the patient's habits in relation to alcohol, drugs and smoking. 請填寫病人飲酒、吸毒或吸煙習慣之詳情。 10. Please describe the underlying cause of Encephalitis. 請指出導致腦炎之原因。 11. Was the disease diagnosed by a specialist neurologist? If so, please provide us with the name and address of neurologist. 病人是否經神經科醫生診斷患有該疾病？如是，請提供該醫生的姓名及地址。 12. Is there any evidence of inflammation in the brain of this patient? Please specify the exact location involved. 病人是否腦部發炎？請註明確切的發炎位置。 13. Is there any sign of permanent neurological deficit due to this disease? For how long? 病人有否因上述疾病導致神經系統永久受損？有關情況為期多久？ 14. Is the disease caused by drug, alcohol, poison, war, active participation in insurrection or riot? Please explain. 該疾病是否由藥物、酒精、毒藥、戰爭、主動參與叛亂或暴動引致？請加以說明。 15. Please give details of radiological investigations, M.R.I., C T scan, laboratory evidence and any other test results for reference. 請提供放射檢驗、磁力共振、電腦斷層掃描、實驗室證據或其他檢驗結果的詳情以供參考。 15. Please provide details of physicians to whom the patient has been referred or attended for this disease. 請提供曾為病人診治是項病症之醫生資料。 (We would be grateful for copies of any relevant medical report that are available ) （敬請提供任何有關醫療報告副本） Name of Physician(s) and/or Hospital(s) Address(es) Date of Consultation(s) and/or Period of Confinement(s) 醫生姓名及／或醫院名稱 地址 診治及／或留院日期 17. If there is any further information which, in your opinion, will assist us in assessing this claim, please furnish such information below. 閣下認為有否其他資料可協助本公司審核是項索償申請？請提供有關資料。 5 Signature 簽署 Date 日期 Qualification 資格 Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司 C24 (11/2025) Name of Physician (with stamp) 醫生姓名（連印章） Address 地址 Tel. No. 電話號碼 1 of 1"});
