window.__KB.push({"t": "CLAIM FORM FOR MAJOR DISEASE OCCUPATIONALLY ACQUIRED HIV 重病保障索償表格 － 因職業引致之 後天免疫力", "f": "C42.pdf", "s": "CLAIM FORM FOR MAJOR DISEASE OCCUPATIONALLY ACQUIRED HIV 重病保障索償表格 － 因職業引致之 後天免疫力缺乏症 Policy No. 保單編號： PART II – This Attending Physician’s Statement must be completed by a qualified and registered physician at the insured’s expense 第二部份 – 本應診醫生報告必須由受保人自費聘請之合資格註冊醫生填寫 1. Name of Patient 病人姓名 2. I.D. Card No. 身份證號碼 3. Age 年齡 4. Are you the patient's usual medical attendant? 閣下是否病人之私人醫生？ No 否 Yes 是 If \"Yes\", give details 若「是」，請填寫有關資料。 Period of Consultation Past Health History 應診期間 病人過往健康情況 5. a) Date on which the patient first consulted you related to the condition (Occupationally Acquired HIV). 病人就是項疾病（因職業引致之後天免疫力缺乏症）首次向閣下求診的 日期（DD日/ MM月/YY年）。 b) What were the symptoms? 病人之病徵？ c) How long had the patient been experiencing these symptoms before the first consultation? 病人在首次求診前已患有此病徵多久？ d) When was the patient informed of the diagnosis? (Please give exact date) 何時通知病人診斷結果?（請填寫準確日期） 6. Give full and exact details of the diagnosis. 請詳盡填寫確實診斷資料。 7. Had the patient any past history of the disease specified above or related illness? 病人過往曾否患有上述疾病或有關疾病？ No 否 Yes 有 If \"Yes\", give details 若「有」，請填寫有關資料。 Name of Attended Physician(s) Date of Consultation Address(es) Exact Diagnosis 應診醫生姓名 診治日期 地址 確實診斷資料 8. Is there anything in the patient’s family history which would have increased the risk of the disease specified above? 病人之家庭背景有否任何增加病人患上上述疾病機 會之事項？ 9. Please give details of the patient's habits in relation to alcohol, drugs and smoking. 請填寫病人飲酒、吸毒或吸煙習慣之詳情。 10. Please describe the extent of the disease. 請描述該病之狀況。 i) Was the infection with HIV resulted from an accident whilst the insured was carrying out normal duties of his/her usual occupation? 受保人是否按其職業進行正常職務時發生意外因而導致感染人體免疫力缺乏病毒？ If “Yes”, please provide the below information. 如“是”，請提供下列資料： Yes 是 No 否 a. Occupation with job duties of the insured. 受保人之職業及其職責： b. When was the accident happened? 該意外於何時發生？ ( / / ) DD/MM/YY 日/月/年 c. How was the accident happened? Please give details. 該意外是怎樣發生？ (請提供詳情。) d. How did you confirm that the aforesaid infection was due to an accident during the course of work? 閣下如何確定該感染是在工作期間因意外感染？ e. When did sero-conversion from HIV negative to HIV positive occured after the said accident? 人體免疫力缺乏病毒之抗體呈陰性反應轉為陽性反應之血清轉 變 於上述意外後何時產生？ f. Was there a negative HIV antibody test done within 14 days from the accident? 意外發生後14日內受保人是否有接受人體免疫力缺乏病毒抗體測試並呈陰性反應？ Yes 是 No 否 ii. Was HIV infection resulted from any of the below means? 人體免疫力缺乏病毒感染是否經由下列途徑導致？ Sexual activity 性行為 Yes 是 No 否 Blood Transfusion as a Recipient 作為接受者接受輸血 Yes 是 No 否 Use of intravenous drug 靜脈藥物注射 Yes 是 No 否 iii. What forms of treatment were rendered? 受保人曾接受哪一種治療？ iv. Present condition and prognosis. 現時之病況及病情進展。 Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司 C42 (11/2025) 1 of 2 Policy No. 保單編號： 11. Please enclose copies of all reports including X-rays, blood tests, other laboratory tests, surgical procedures and any relevant hospital reports that are available. 請提供所有報告包括 X 光檢查，驗血，其他化驗報告及手術報告等，或任何有關的醫院 報告。 12. Please provide details of physicians to whom the patient has been referred or attended for this disease. 請提供曾為病人診治是項病症之醫生資料。 (We would be grateful for copies of any relevant medical report that are available ) （敬請提供任何有關醫療報告副本） Name of Physician(s) and/or Hospital(s) Address(es) Date of Consultation(s) and/or Period of Confinement(s) 醫生姓名及／或醫院名稱 地址 診治及／或留院日期 13. If there is any further information which, in your opinion, will assist us in assessing this claim, please furnish such information below. 閣下認為有否其他資料可協助本公司審核是項索償申請？請提供有關資料。 5 Signature 簽署 Date 日期 Qualification 資格 Name of Physician (with stamp) 醫生姓名（連印章） Address 地址 Tel. No. 電話號碼 Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司 C42 (11/2025) 2 of 2"});
