window.__KB.push({"t": "To From Date : Manulife (International) Ltd. : : Re: Group Policy No. _________ ", "f": "團體保障轉移協議書（樣本）.pdf", "s": "To From Date : Manulife (International) Ltd. : : Re: Group Policy No. _________ This is to confirm that the following members under the captioned group policy are no longer working at ___________________________________ (Name of Existing Employer) “the Previous Company” and will be transferred to _________________________________ (Name of New Employer) “the New Company” with effect from ______________ (DD/MM/YYYY). We hereby apply for the replacement of the captioned group policy by a new group policy to be issued to the New Company “the New Policy” to continue the same policy coverage in respect of the following members. It is understood that the captioned group policy of the Previous Company will upon completion of this replacement process be terminated. We hereby apply for the transfer of any unused premium paid by the Previous Company under the captioned group policy to the New Policy and we understand that any waiver of underwriting requirements for the above replacement and in particular for the said members to be enrolled in the New Policy will be conditional upon the fact that all these members are the same and their employment are transferred from the Previous Company to the New Company with same or similar job duties. Member List Member Name Employment Date with the New Company It is understood and agreed that all claims paid under the captioned group policy of the Previous Company in respect of the above members shall be treated as paid claims in respect of the same members under the New Policy for the purpose of determining the maximum benefit that the said members are entitled under the Benefit Schedule of the New Policy. Yours sincerely, __________________________________ (Signed by Authorized person of Existing Employer with company stamp) _________________________________ (Signed by Authorized person of New Employer with company stamp) (Version 06/2016)"});
